data.description:
Welcome to 9094 E BC Ave! This 3 bed, 1 1/2 bath near Gull Lake is sure to impress with recent renovations and thoughtful finishes throughout. On the main floor you'll find an updated kitchen with stainless appliances, tile backsplash, large farmhouse sink, and attractive quartz countertops. The spacious living room features newly refinished hardwood floors, gas fireplace, and large windows offering tons of natural light. There is easy access to the back porch off the kitchen and dining room ready for spring time!

Upstairs you'll find three bedrooms offering plenty of natural light, and a recently remodeled bathroom. Downstairs there is an extra living area, access to the garage, and a laundry/utility room. The large back yard offers a great mix of sun & shade, a chicken coop and room for a garden. That's not all! This home has a great location nestled close to Gull Lake with an easy drive into Downtown Richland, or a quick trip down Gull into Kalamazoo.

A lot to love! Schedule your showing today!
